BACKEND API ROUTES

Root
GET / - loads React web app, main homepage


Session/Auth
POST /api/session   (new login)
DELETE /api/session   (Logout)


User
POST /api/user  (Create New User if time allows)
GET /api/user/:id	(If not, just go with DEMO account)
PATCH /api/user/:id    (Update your own business, require login)



Businesses
GET /api/business (Index: with constraints. maybe all businesses in a certain location?)
POST /api/business  (Create New business)
GET /api/business/:id	(Business show page)
PATCH /api/business/:id    (Update your own business, require login)

Reviews
GET /api/reviews(with business id?) (Index: with constraints? See all of your own reviews? All reviews of a business?)
POST /api/reviews  (Post New review)
GET /api/reviews/:id	(Show individual review)
PATCH /api/reviews/:id    (Update your own review, require login)

FRONT END ROUTES

Homepage


Search Results Page

Business Show page

New Business Form

New Review form
